@Next "M5346"
@Prev "M5344"
@Toc "M534"

Select Range...
...............

Opens a special requester which enables you to select a  range  within
the  catalog  buffer.  All  thumbnails  of  this  range  will be shown
afterwards.


@EndNode

@Node "M5346" "ImageDeskE.guide/M5346"
@Prev "M5345"
@Toc "M534"

Catalog Browser
...............

The @{i}Catalog Browser@{ui} provides a quick overview of a catalog.  It  makes
no  use  of  the  catalog  buffer so it asks for a catalog file before
opening its window. This window shows the global catalog data  in  the
upper area:

   @{b}*@{ub} catalog name

   @{b}*@{ub} number of entries

   @{b}*@{ub} basic thumbnail sizes

   @{b}*@{ub} directory path of the images

In the middle part of the window the thumbnails image  is  figured  on
the left side. next to it the data of the current thumbnails is shown:

   @{b}*@{ub} picture name

   @{b}*@{ub} picture type

   @{b}*@{ub} picture height, width, depth

   @{b}*@{ub} colortable information

On the right side a listview gadget is located in which all  available
thumbnail entries are listed. Switching to another thumbnail is either
possible by clicking it with the mouse button or by using  the  cursor
keys.

Bellow this five buttons are located:

   @{b}*@{ub} Load New - Loads a new catalog into the browser

   @{b}*@{ub} To Desk - Copies the current thumbnail to the desk

   @{b}*@{ub} View Image - Views the corresponding picture of the current
     thumbnail

   @{b}*@{ub} AREXX - Calls the @{i}Default AREXX Script@{ui}

   @{b}*@{ub} Close - leaves the browser window


@EndNode

@Node "M535" "ImageDeskE.guide/M535"
@Next "M536"
@Prev "M534"
@Toc "M53"

View Images
-----------

The menu items contained here serve for viewing pictures. The
adjustments made in the @{b}Viewer Prefs@{ub} are responsible for the viewers
behavior.  All internal viewers can be interrupted at any time by
pressing the @{b}<ESC>@{ub}-Key.


 @{" Single File         A V " Link "M5351"}      
 @{" Path Contents       A P " Link "M5352"}      
 @{" Selected Thumbnails A T " Link "M5353"} 


