IDREQUEST
---------

@{i}Syntax:@{ui} @{b}IDREQUEST <Gadget1>|<Gadgeet2>|...|<Gadget0> <Text>@{ub}

@{i}Description:@{ui} Opens an intuition requester containing the body <Text>
and the button texts <Gadget1>, <Gadget2>,..., <Gadget0>.

@{i}Result:@{ui} Number of selected gadget (1,2,...,0) (Integer).

@{i}Example:@{ui}
     IDREQUEST "YES|NO" '"Do you want to exit?"'
     if( Result = 1 ) then exit


@EndNode

