ERRORMSG
--------

@{i}Syntax:@{ui} @{b}ERRORMSG <Text>@{ub}

@{i}Description:@{ui} Opens ImageDesk's  standard  error  requester,  containing
the  error message <Text>.

@{i}Result:@{ui} NULL

@{i}Example:@{ui} @{b}ERRORMSG '"Last command failed!"'@{ub}


